$terraform init    -->    Will check the configuration file and intialize the .tf file

$terraform plan    -->    Will show the actions that will be carried out by terraform to create the resources

$terraform apply    -->    Will display the execution plan once again, then ask the user to confirm by typing "yes" to confirm

$terraform show    -->    Running within the configuration directory to see the details of the resources that we just created

$terraform destroy    -->    Will delete the resources
